## Step 2 — Install NGINX Gateway Fabric (NGF) via Helm

```bash
helm install ngf oci://ghcr.io/nginx/charts/nginx-gateway-fabric \
  --create-namespace \
  -n nginx-gateway
```

Verify the control-plane pod is running:

```bash
kubectl get pods -n nginx-gateway
```

Check the auto-created GatewayClass:

```bash
kubectl get gatewayclass
```
Note the exact name shown (commonly `nginx`) — you'll reference it in Step 5.

